  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Peel and slice the apples, and place them in a baking dish.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix the custard, flour, and vanilla extract.",
    "Pour the custard mixture over the apples, and sprinkle with brown sugar.",
    "Mix the oats, melted butter, and crisp in a bowl to create the topping.",
